import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import {
  Stack,
  Dialog,
  DialogContent,
  DialogTitle,
  DialogContentText,
  TextField,
  DialogActions,
  Button
} from '@mui/material';

const Settings = (props) => {
  return (
    <Dialog {...this.props}>
      <DialogTitle>Subscribe</DialogTitle>
      <DialogContent>
        <DialogContentText>
          To subscribe to this website, please enter your email address here. We
          will send updates occasionally.
        </DialogContentText>
        <TextField
          autoFocus
          margin="dense"
          id="name"
          label="Email Address"
          type="email"
          fullWidth
          variant="standard"
        />
      </DialogContent>
      <DialogActions>
        <Button onClick={handleClose}>Cancel</Button>
        <Button onClick={handleClose}>Subscribe</Button>
      </DialogActions>
    </Dialog>
  );
}
export default Settings;
